WHY?

34:39.648 --> 34:41.780
[SOBBING]

34:41.780 --> 34:44.753
WHY?

34:59.668 --> 35:01.770
DEVIL SAID NO, HUH?

35:01.770 --> 35:03.772
I TRIED.

35:05.704 --> 35:09.478
YEAH. WELL, IT WAS
A LONG SHOT, ANYWAY,
RIGHT?

35:09.478 --> 35:11.710
RUN.

35:11.710 --> 35:12.211
RUN?

35:12.211 --> 35:13.642
RUN AWAY.
JUST GET OUT OF HERE.

35:13.642 --> 35:14.443
FORGET ABOUT THE TITLE.

35:14.443 --> 35:16.745
IF YOU DISAPPEAR
SOMEPLACE I CAN'T FIND YOU,

35:16.745 --> 35:17.716
YOU ARE FREE.

35:17.716 --> 35:19.218
CAN'T DO THAT, CHIEF.

35:19.218 --> 35:20.319
WHY? WHY NOT?

35:20.319 --> 35:21.850
COME ON, CAN'T FORGET
ABOUT THE TITLE.

35:21.850 --> 35:24.353
WHO CARES ABOUT
SOME BOXING MATCH?

35:24.353 --> 35:25.654
YOU GOT OUT OF HELL.

35:25.654 --> 35:28.357
ISN'T THAT MORE IMPORTANT
THAN A GAME?

35:28.357 --> 35:29.658
NO.

35:30.459 --> 35:33.462
I REMEMBER
THE END OF MY LIFE.

35:34.703 --> 35:39.608
I KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO LOOK BACK
AND REALIZE...

35:39.608 --> 35:41.570
YOU THREW IT ALL AWAY.

35:41.570 --> 35:43.812
I TURNED MYSELF INTO
A PIECE OF GARBAGE.

35:43.812 --> 35:46.675
AND THAT
KIND OF REGRET...

35:47.776 --> 35:50.779
I CAN'T LET THAT
BE ALL THAT I AM.

35:50.779 --> 35:53.522
IT'S NOT JUST A GAME.

35:53.522 --> 35:54.883
I WIN THIS TITLE
FAIR AND SQUARE,

35:54.883 --> 35:56.885
IT'LL PROVE THAT
I'M NOT ALL ROTTEN

35:56.885 --> 35:58.487
AND WASH AWAY
ALL MY MISTAKES.

35:58.487 --> 36:01.490
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS
TO BE A GOOD PERSON.

36:01.490 --> 36:02.361
GO JOIN THE PEACE CORPS,

36:02.361 --> 36:03.792
BUILD HOUSES
FOR POOR PEOPLE--

36:03.792 --> 36:05.334
ANYTHING BUT THIS.

36:05.334 --> 36:07.866
FIGHTING'S
THE ONLY THING
I'M GOOD AT, SAM.

36:07.866 --> 36:10.469
Devil:
I HEAR A LOT OF TALKING...

36:10.469 --> 36:13.572
BUT I DON'T SEE
A LOT OF FIGHTING.

36:13.572 --> 36:14.273
HEH!

36:14.273 --> 36:15.704
I KNOW HIM.
YEAH.

36:15.704 --> 36:17.446
HE'S THE GUY
WHO PAID YOU OFF,

36:17.446 --> 36:18.747
ALSO KNOWN AS
THE DEVIL.

36:18.747 --> 36:22.411
YOU KNOW, BOYS,
AS FAR AS I CAN TELL,

36:22.411 --> 36:23.682
THERE ARE TWO WAYS
THIS IS GONNA END.

36:23.682 --> 36:27.786
ONE OF YOU WILL FIND HIS WAY
BACK TO HELL...

36:27.786 --> 36:29.888
OR ONE OF YOU
WILL BE DEAD.

36:29.888 --> 36:34.723
IT DOESN'T MATTER TO ME
WHICH WAY IT GOES.

36:34.723 --> 36:37.526
BUT I RECOMMEND SOMEBODY
START THROWING SOME PUNCHES

36:37.526 --> 36:39.898
BEFORE I LOSE MY PATIENCE.

36:40.799 --> 36:42.901
NO. LOOK. WE'RE NOT
GONNA--UNH!

36:42.901 --> 36:45.674
YES! THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

36:45.674 --> 36:46.805
RED! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

36:46.805 --> 36:49.538
WHOA. WHAT--WHAT--RED!
RED!

36:49.538 --> 36:53.282
WE DON'T HAVE
TO DO THIS, OK?

36:53.282 --> 36:55.644
HA HA HA!

37:03.252 --> 37:04.723
MAKE IT LOOK GOOD.
WHAT?

37:04.723 --> 37:06.555
I LAID DOWN ONCE BEFORE
FOR THE WRONG REASONS.

37:06.555 --> 37:08.497
I'M GONNA LAY DOWN
FOR THE RIGHT ONES.

37:08.497 --> 37:09.828
HEY, STOP CLINCHING,
LADIES.

37:09.828 --> 37:12.501
THIS IS A FIGHT,
NOT A DANCE HALL.

37:12.501 --> 37:16.405
RED, NO.
SO MAKE
IT LOOK GOOD.

37:31.450 --> 37:35.824
ALL RIGHT! WOW!
THAT WAS INTENSE.

37:35.824 --> 37:36.855
YOU KNOW,
I DON'T MIND TELLING YOU,

37:36.855 --> 37:40.889
I WOULD HAVE BET
AGAINST YOU IF I WAS
A BETTING MAN.

37:43.492 --> 37:43.832
TAKE THEM.

37:43.832 --> 37:47.035
AW! COME ON, SAMMY,
DON'T BE LIKE THAT.

37:47.035 --> 37:48.697
SAVOR THE VICTORY.

37:48.697 --> 37:51.400
EYE OF THE TIGER,
SAMMY!

37:51.400 --> 37:53.672
EYE OF THE TIGER.

38:03.512 --> 38:04.052
WHAT'S GOING ON?

38:04.052 --> 38:05.984
BENJI'S BEEN
TALKING TO THESE
GRIEF COUNSELORS

38:05.984 --> 38:07.356
FOR, LIKE, AN HOUR.

38:07.356 --> 38:10.559
HE'S PRETTY BROKEN UP
ABOUT NINA.

38:10.559 --> 38:12.521
LOOK OUT, MAN.

38:12.521 --> 38:16.625
WE'RE GONNA NEED
COFFEE AND POUND CAKE
IN HERE, PLEASE.

38:16.625 --> 38:20.399
I'M GONNA TAKE A SHOT
AT THIS. BEN?

38:20.399 --> 38:22.831
CAN I TALK TO YOU
FOR A SECOND?

38:22.831 --> 38:24.603
BEN, I KNOW THIS
HAS BEEN HARD ON YOU,

38:24.603 --> 38:26.835
BUT I NEED YOU TO TAKE
ALL YOUR PERSONAL FEELINGS,

38:26.835 --> 38:30.679
JUST SHOVE THEM ASIDE,
AND ANSWER ME WITH CLARITY.

38:30.679 --> 38:33.342
DO YOU THINK NINA
WAS TRYING TO MURDER ME?

38:33.342 --> 38:35.584
SHE SAID
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

38:35.584 --> 38:38.717
I THOUGHT ABOUT IT,
AND I BELIEVE HER.

38:38.717 --> 38:41.690
I MEAN, I KNOW
I'VE HAD BAD JUDGMENT
IN THE PAST,

38:41.690 --> 38:44.923
BUT I KNOW
I'M RIGHT ABOUT NINA.

38:46.355 --> 38:48.397
OK.

38:48.397 --> 38:49.358
OK?

38:49.358 --> 38:50.759
NINA'S MADE HER MISTAKES.

38:50.759 --> 38:52.361
SCARY, EVIL MISTAKES.

38:52.361 --> 38:54.403
BUT I TRUST YOU, BEN.

38:54.403 --> 38:55.664
AND IF YOU SEE
SOMETHING GOOD IN HER,

38:55.664 --> 38:56.865
I HAVE TO BELIEVE YOU,

38:56.865 --> 39:01.910
BECAUSE I'VE SEEN GOOD
IN SOME UNLIKELY PLACES
RECENTLY.

39:01.910 --> 39:03.041
THANKS, SAM.

39:03.041 --> 39:03.972
NO PROBLEM.

39:03.972 --> 39:06.375
HUG IT OUT. LET GO.

39:06.375 --> 39:08.417
GO GET YOUR DEMON.

39:08.417 --> 39:09.748
THAT WAS SWEET OF YOU.

39:09.748 --> 39:10.419
THANK YOU.

39:10.419 --> 39:13.922
I HOPE HE DOESN'T
GET EATEN.
ME, TOO.

39:14.883 --> 39:17.125
NINA, I'M BACK.

39:17.125 --> 39:20.128
BABY, WE NEED TO TALK.

39:21.660 --> 39:23.862
WHOA. OOH! OOH!

39:23.862 --> 39:25.864
[ROAR]

39:25.864 --> 39:27.065
AH...UH...

39:27.065 --> 39:29.838
GREAT NEWS, HONEY.
WE CAN GET BACK TOGETHER.

39:29.838 --> 39:30.869
[SNARLING]

39:30.869 --> 39:31.540
NINA, I'M SORRY.

39:31.540 --> 39:34.773
I LISTENED TO MY FRIENDS
INSTEAD OF LISTENING TO MYSELF.

39:34.773 --> 39:37.406
I BELIEVED IN YOU.
I ALWAYS BELIEVED IN YOU.

39:37.406 --> 39:39.678
I KNOW YOU'RE NOT A MONSTER.

39:39.678 --> 39:41.780
YOU'RE MY GIRL...

39:41.780 --> 39:44.613
MY SWEET, BEAUTIFUL...

39:44.613 --> 39:45.914
CRAZY-ASS GIRL.

39:45.914 --> 39:49.758
AH...GETTING A LITTLE
LIGHT-HEADED NOW.

39:49.758 --> 39:54.823
ACTUALLY, I'M GETTING
TUNNEL VISION NOW.

40:04.873 --> 40:05.834
I'M SORRY, NINA.

40:05.834 --> 40:09.107
PLEASE GIVE ME
ANOTHER CHANCE.

40:13.912 --> 40:15.944
YOU'RE FORGIVEN.

40:15.944 --> 40:17.816
HMM.

40:19.848 --> 40:22.150
Man: ♪ OH, DANNY BOY ♪

40:22.150 --> 40:28.126
♪ THE PIPES, THE PIPES
ARE CALLING ♪

40:28.126 --> 40:31.500
♪ FROM GLEN TO GLEN... ♪

40:31.500 --> 40:32.501
UNBELIEVABLE.

40:32.501 --> 40:34.432
Sock:
ALMS FOR LESTER.

40:34.432 --> 40:36.765
ALMS FOR LES--
YEAH, THANK YOU.

40:36.765 --> 40:38.036
THANK YOU. THANK YOU.

40:38.036 --> 40:38.707
WHAT IS THIS?

40:38.707 --> 40:40.539
WE'RE THROWING A WAKE
FOR LES NESSMAN.

40:40.539 --> 40:41.970
WHY ARE WE THROWING
A WAKE FOR LES NESSMAN?

40:41.970 --> 40:45.774
BECAUSE HE WAS MURDERED
BY YOUR GIRLFRIEND.

40:45.774 --> 40:47.075
YOU'RE SUCH A MORON.

40:47.075 --> 40:48.547
YOU GUYS KICKING IN?

40:48.547 --> 40:48.847
FOR WHAT?

40:48.847 --> 40:50.779
LES' MOM SAYS THEY'RE
HAVING A REALLY ROUGH TIME

40:50.779 --> 40:52.581
WITH THE FUNERAL EXPENSES.

40:52.581 --> 40:53.582
TRICKY TIME TO DIE.

40:53.582 --> 40:55.824
DON'T DIE,
IF YOU'RE THINKING ABOUT IT.

40:55.824 --> 40:56.985
YOU'RE KIDDING.

40:56.985 --> 40:57.686
YES, ANDI,

40:57.686 --> 41:02.130
I LOVE TO JOKE ABOUT
PEOPLE WHO DIED PENNILESS.

41:02.130 --> 41:03.461
[SCOFF]

41:03.461 --> 41:04.793
OK.

41:04.793 --> 41:06.765
A 5? REALLY?

41:06.765 --> 41:08.737
IT'S A 5, EVERYBODY.

41:08.737 --> 41:10.098
OK.

41:10.098 --> 41:11.039
HERE.

41:11.039 --> 41:12.040
AHH. I THANK YOU.

41:12.040 --> 41:14.102
AND LES NESSMAN
THANKS YOU.

41:14.102 --> 41:15.073
NOW,
IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME,

41:15.073 --> 41:18.777
I JUST HAVE A COUPLE THINGS
TO ATTEND TO.

41:18.777 --> 41:20.979
OHH.

41:23.051 --> 41:24.883
HEY. UH, WHY DON'T YOU
GRAB US A TABLE?

41:24.883 --> 41:27.956
I'LL GRAB US
A COUPLE DRINKS.
OK.

41:27.956 --> 41:28.887
TWO BEERS.

41:28.887 --> 41:30.519
OH, PUT THOSE
ON MY TAB? PLEASE?

41:30.519 --> 41:32.220
NO, NO, NO,
I'LL PAY FOR IT.

41:32.220 --> 41:33.922
OH, JEEZ, SAM.

41:33.922 --> 41:35.764
I'M JUST TRYING
TO BE FRIENDLY.

41:35.764 --> 41:36.895
WHAT, DO YOU WANT
SOMETHING?

41:36.895 --> 41:39.768
WELL, YOU SEEMED DOWN
AFTER THE SABATINO FIGHT.

41:39.768 --> 41:42.531
SO I JUST CAME BY
TO CHECK ON YOU.

41:42.531 --> 41:42.971
NO, YOU DIDN'T.

41:42.971 --> 41:45.874
YOU CAME HER TO GLOAT
OVER FORCING ME TO SEND
RED BACK TO HELL.

41:45.874 --> 41:49.538
WELL, THE TWO WANTS
ARE NOT MUTUALLY EXCLUSIVE.

41:49.538 --> 41:50.879
[CHUCKLE]

41:50.879 --> 41:52.711
TO VICTORY.

41:54.112 --> 41:55.584
THANKS.

41:55.584 --> 41:56.514
YOU KNOW, SAMMY,

41:56.514 --> 41:57.916
YOU CAN MAKE IT
A LOT EASIER ON YOURSELF

41:57.916 --> 42:01.049
IF YOU JUST REMEMBER
THE FIRST RULE:

42:01.049 --> 42:05.193
I'M ALWAYS GOING TO WIN.

42:05.193 --> 42:05.854
[CHUCKLE]

42:05.854 --> 42:09.998
AND I HATE TO SEE YOU
TEARING YOURSELF APART
LIKE THIS.

42:09.998 --> 42:13.061
RED THREW THE FIGHT.

42:13.061 --> 42:13.902
HE LET ME WIN.

42:13.902 --> 42:16.665
HEY, DON'T KID
A KIDDER, KIDDO.

42:16.665 --> 42:17.706
WHY WOULD HE DO THAT?

42:17.706 --> 42:18.937
BECAUSE HE WANTED
TO GO BACK TO HELL

42:18.937 --> 42:22.641
KNOWING HE DID
SOMETHING GOOD,
SOMETHING WORTHWHILE.

42:22.641 --> 42:25.974
SO HE SACRIFICED HIMSELF
TO SAVE ME.

42:25.974 --> 42:27.746
HE GOT HIS WISH.

42:27.746 --> 42:33.251
SO IN A WAY,
YOU DID SOMETHING GOOD.

42:34.753 --> 42:37.055
WEIRD, HUH?

42:38.987 --> 42:40.659
[CHUCKLE]
